Justice Taiwo Taiwo of the Federal High Court sitting in Abuja, on Monday, granted the EFCC’s prayer to freeze the FCMB Operational Account number: 0998552074 of the Bauchi State government. The judge, which adjourned the matter to Sept.3, urged the commission to put the party concern on notice of the order within 21 days. Details later…  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .